headline: Zimmer Biomet to Present at Citi's 2024 Global Healthcare Conference
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE and SIX: ZBH) today announced that members of the Zimmer Biomet management team will participate in the Citi Global Healthcare Conference on December 5, 2024, with a fireside chat at 8:45 a.m. ET.
